| Name           | Hex       | Description                                                                 |
| :------------- | :-------- | :-------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Forge Charcoal** | `#333132` | **Primary Dark.** A deep, warm grey. The color of cooled metal and shadow.  |
| **Ember Gold**   | `#FFB800` | **Primary Action.** Bright, energetic orange-yellow. For CTAs, and warnings. |
| **Circuit Teal** | `#00F0FF` | **Primary Tech.** A vibrant cyan. For UI highlights, holograms, and energy. |
